  [Unidentified correspondent] Your Excellency, concerning the 
devaluation of the CFA franc, in concrete terms, what economic 
benefits can Chad expect from Nigeria? 
  [Deby] [Words indistinct] and even on this specific point, 
Nigeria is an oil-producing country. We have great difficulties 
in this specific field, so we expressed the wish to see Nigeria 
helping us to procure this product. What we are expecting from 
the Nigerian authorities is a positive reaction to our request. 
[end recording] 

