94 </F>

<F P=103> AB0402120094 </F>
<F P=104>  Kinshasa Voix du Zaire </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> French </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] A new political party has just been approved. It is 
the National Christian Social Democratic Party [PDSCN]. The 
ethics of PDSCN are founded on Christian moral principles and 
rules and all positive human values. The PDSCN militates for 
the restoration of a truly pluralistic democracy in a climate of 
tolerance and public morality that are conducive to the 
harmonious development of the nation. 

