<F P=104>  Johannesburg Radio South Africa Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The ANC [African National Congress] says those who 
had hoped to see a new National Party [NP] grappling with the 
realities of the country will have been bitterly disappointed by 
the party's election manifesto. The manifesto was announced 
earlier at the NP federal congress at Kempton Park. 
