<H3> <TI>   Meetings Between Oakley, Faction Leaders Reported </TI></H3>
<H4>   SNA Deputy Chairman Meets With Oakley </H4>
<F P=102> AB0502192894 (Clandestine) Radio Mogadishu Voice of the 
Great Somali People in Somali 1700 GMT 5 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> AB0502192894 </F>
