in Cuito, but you should not blame the resumption of fighting in 
Cuito on the government forces. UNITA has been engaging in 
offensive operations in several parts of the country and, 
obviously, the government has to react. I hope the fighting 
that resumed on the 2d in Cuito will end soon. [end recording] 
